Building diy:

cd diy

Configure diy:
If parallel netcdf is not installed on your system
./configure --disable-pnetcdf
To configure without BIL:
./configure --disable-bil
A full configure
./configure
The options for the configure command are available by:
./configure --help

Build diy:
make

Install diy:
make install


